 #  Changelog
 
## 2026-05-25
 
### Bugfix
  * Fixed an issue on the "Print Preprocessing" page: when more than 4 preset filaments were available, users could not select the excess filaments to match with the mounted filaments on the device.
  * Fixed an issue where printing could not be initiated normally when the preset filament density was set to 0.
### 问题修复
  * 修复了预设耗材超过 4 个时，超过部分无法在 "打印预处理页" 选择设备挂载耗材的问题
  * 修复了打印预设耗材密度为 0 时，无法正常开始打印的问题
